{"tid":1917262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★「油不如水」---原油每升約1.47港元，蒸餾水1升約10港元","createTime":"2020-03-09T11:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T11:56:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c510379c31292671ba8ca2355fda6f6e09a2495","tid":1917262,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"綜合媒體報道，隨着油價一度狂瀉至每桶30美元，這是甚麼概念？就是一桶礦泉水的價格原來是原油的6倍，一桶可口可樂則較原油貴72倍！<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，一桶原油約158.98升，以紐約期油每桶30美元計算，換算後油價為每升0.19美元，即每升大約1.47港元。再看看蒸餾水，以市面上1升水價格約10港元計，是國際原油價格的6倍有多，名副其實「油不如水」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200309/bkn-20200309175304317-0309_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200309%2Fbkn-20200309175304317-0309_00842_001.html&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=498a6a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200309/bkn-20200309175304317-0309_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f015b4599074ee5022513cfa974d2f680c237bb1","tid":1917262,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45eb00beaf406c205bea03f29c72b0b8e97de28","tid":1917262,"uid":118781,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"出面30蚊  <br />\n習近平同普京買要130蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da32dd54721aa3c5795e61e16917cb56fd912ca","tid":1917262,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a45eb00beaf406c205bea03f29c72b0b8e97de28","tid":1917262,"uid":118781,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco